**Investment Disclaimer:** Robo-advisors invest in securities that involve risk, including possible loss of principal. Past performance does not guarantee future results. Mean-variance optimization, Black-Litterman, and Gordon Growth Model outputs are projections based on assumptions that may prove incorrect. Tax-loss harvesting benefits depend on individual tax circumstances. Consider consulting a tax professional and/or fiduciary financial advisor before making investment decisions. SIPC protection covers securities in case of broker-dealer failure, not investment losses.
</Warning>

